{
  "stem": "8252.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that point, they told me later on there were already other trains, and they could place her in, in a passenger car.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Before she left, I gave an a-- an address of-- a friend of mine married a Jew from Vienna and his parents' address, I had.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said to my mother, if you have any problems while you are in Vienna-- because she was going to Vienna and then into Italy-- see these people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my mother is gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I am all alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I have to get a visa to any country to get out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So the Italians will let me in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Italy does not want us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I find a Greek consul, who was not a consul anymore, but he has all those stamps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And for an amount of money he gives me an entry visa to Greece with a solemn promise that I will never show my face in Greece.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So here I am this way and my friend, who had the same papers-- both of us, we had the same papers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And in December 1939, before the ghetto was established in Lodz, I get on a train with this friend of mine and we sit in a passenger car, by the way.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "By that time already, passenger cars were available.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We roll our overcoats.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It's cold, so we have overcoats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We roll our overcoats so that my yellow armband doesn't show.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we sit there, and we travel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And soon the compartment-- you know the European compartments are for just few people-- is empty and we just sit, the two of us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we are in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The names start changing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it's absolutely dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
